{"tid":485290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子稱未滿十三歲時與前未婚夫性交 官指事主或記錯時間判被告脫罪","createTime":"2017-12-01T00:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T20:59:39.000Z","uid":8171,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f7fa5ff025012599a4b9e81937991b5fda59125b","tid":485290,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/080122_82395ec6a0a0f1d85643c088cc1e28a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F080122_82395ec6a0a0f1d85643c088cc1e28a8.jpg&h=17a1294b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女子指控前未婚夫在13年前她未滿13歲時，在她自願的情況下與她3度性交。案件在區域法院經審訊後，裁定前未婚夫被控的3項「與13歲以下女童非法性交」罪罪脫。法官認為女事主所指的事情並非虛構，但事隔多年，無可避免對案發時間的記憶有偏差。<br />\n<br />\n法官裁決時指，案件只倚賴女事主的證供，並沒有其他佐證，而事主曾在被告提出分手後，向被告發短訊表示準備的「4周年禮物」會令他很驚喜，又指「你之後會好憎我」、「會令你身敗名裂」、「我得唔到嘅嘢寧願揼爛佢，都唔會畀第二個」等，反映事主存在報復心態，加上事主正正是在兩人復合4周年的日子，到警署報案。<br />\n<br />\n法官續指，案件關鍵因素在於兩人性交的時候，事主是否已滿13歲或16歲，認為事主有可能記錯兩人發生性行為的時間，遂判李罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n事主在早前作供指，與被告在13年前的中學時期已成為情侶，其後分手，至2012年復合，其後更合資賺買物業及談婚論嫁。惟婚前被告提出分手，事主要求復合不果，其後向社工傾談透露曾在12歲時與李發生性行為，並於今年報案。"},{"pid":"efaa735c39af41a8db2999cf3b1f48764f993f96","tid":485290,"uid":68132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:07:56.000Z","msg":"就算係真都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae1febb64ab9dd462263dc9cf3658f9d9ce0500","tid":485290,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:16:40.000Z","msg":"隻雞輸打贏要抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106051fd64a1154bc85990c7f3ecf573d3946a9e","tid":485290,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba4aee82e4729f4e5d7ef8c95e1292c3219aa59","tid":485290,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/081834_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F081834_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=796c4532&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15aa93076bdca165ecff233ec02ffb65714ec417","tid":485290,"uid":34760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:19:15.000Z","msg":"事實證明要即時報案 之後任你點講都得 咁都判得入全香港男人等仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4fec3db67b61aa04e0e291da467db489adcd0e","tid":485290,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:19:20.000Z","msg":"屌臭雞  比假口供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又屈鳩條仔"},{"pid":"f8501f2d70c852145172d1d4824d597754a0b0f5","tid":485290,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:19:37.000Z","msg":"又一單案例證明呂小姐單野值得懷疑"},{"pid":"782c22fd6bb4ec182b2a93c68766a162eed6335e","tid":485290,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/10/13/32936_20161013105450_57fef77a32a06.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F13%2F32936_20161013105450_57fef77a32a06.gif&h=29025a40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d42b6a7bc572cfa682dc63598ebc55dc56fa8137","tid":485290,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as